<h1 class="govuk-heading-l datagovuk-heading-l">Deaths</h1>

<p class="govuk-body-m datagovuk-body">This data includes registered deaths by age, sex, selected underlying causes of death and the leading causes of death in England and Wales up to 2024.  The data contains death rates and death registrations by area of residence and single year of age. This dataset is owned by the Office for National Statistics (ONS).</p>



